"Please install Git. If using Homebrew: brew install git, or install Xcode "
"Command Line Tools: xcode-select --install"
msgstr ""
"Instale o Git. Se estiver usando Homebrew: brew install git, ou instale as "
"Ferramentas de Linha de Comando do Xcode: xcode-select --install"

